---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Privacy Policy — Deskbly" description="How Deskbly collects, uses, and protects your data." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p><em>Last updated: March 13, 2026</em></p>

			<p>At Deskbly ("we", "us", or "our"), we respect your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you visit deskbly.com.</p>

			<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
			<p>We collect minimal information:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Analytics data:</strong> We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our site. This includes pages visited, time on site, device type, and approximate location (country/city level). This data is anonymous.</li>
				<li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Google Analytics and our affiliate partners may place cookies on your device to track visits and referrals.</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>To understand which content is most useful to our readers</li>
				<li>To improve our site and articles</li>
				<li>To track affiliate referrals (so we can earn commissions when you buy products through our links)</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
			<p>Deskbly participates in affiliate programs, including the Amazon Associates Program. When you click a product link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. These commissions help us keep the site running.</p>

			<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
			<p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — for website analytics</li>
				<li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — for hosting and CDN</li>
				<li><strong>Amazon Associates</strong> — for affiliate links</li>
			</ul>
			<p>Each of these services has their own privacy policies.</p>

			<h2>Your Choices</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>You can disable cookies in your browser settings</li>
				<li>You can use an ad blocker to prevent tracking</li>
				<li>You can opt out of Google Analytics using Google's opt-out browser add-on</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
			<p>Our site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

			<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
			<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will post any changes on this page with an updated date.</p>

			<h2>Contact</h2>
			<p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@deskbly.com">hello@deskbly.com</a>.</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
